    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor is so old school and just keeps telling me the same thing over and over. i feel like i should have more control over my own body. if i just really commit to the natural stuff, like lots of garlic and the greens, isnt that just doing what the medicine is trying to do but in a healthier way? like, can't i just taper off the warfarin slowly while I ramp up the supplements so my body adjusts?",
